{
  "stem": "11611.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If it did nothing else, it established an irrefutable historical record of German conduct for a period of about 12 years, which stands there still as a monument to people who have now gotten around to say nothing ever happened.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the defense of superior orders was knocked down and reduced to a mitigating factor, and the charges, I thought, were interesting.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Although there was a lot of dispute about them, the-- the basic Nuremberg charge was crimes against the peace, aggressive war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the real thrust of Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's still stands as a-- a testimonial to the principal that you cannot freely invade your neighbors at discretion, that-- that is a war crime, and of course, it's a war crime, which has been violated by every country in the succeeding 50 years.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it remains a war crime and something of a dead letter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, in practical effect, the Nuremberg Trials have not had a great deal of impact, although after a rocky start with people attacking one aspect or another, they've come to be accepted as-- as established international law, adhered to, in-- in theory, by all the countries of the world.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't seem to have affected conduct at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There has not been a major war on the scale of World War I or World War II, but to the extent there have been wars, there have been wars with very little justification and marked by very little civilized conduct.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, it may be a contradiction in terms to talk about a civilized war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the so-called international community is a state of anarchy in which each state is an independent power, and if you've got industrial and military power, you do exactly as you please unless you face a counterveiling power.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
